Did you watching seaspiracy?
Did you hate it?
Did you think it was BS?
Did it open your eyes and make you want to change your eating habits?

@iamjuliawheeler  and i sat down with Ali Tabrizi the director and host of what had become one of @netflix most controversial documentaries and asked him the hard questions that everyone wants to know. 
Here’s what Julia had to say:

Well, I didn’t hold back during this interview and had to throw everything under the bus, including @iamalitabrizi the Director of @netflix top ten and highly controversial films, @seaspiracy with @pauldegelder who spent the majority of the interview looking like I just slapped him in the face. This film is out of control. But the allegations around the misinformation that the film presents are even more out of control. Watch @seaspiracy and listen to our latest podcast on @thedirtdownunder where we go deep and uncover the truth behind these crazy allegations (link in bio)  #podcast #freediver #hardcore #owch #boom

I’m pretty sure if any of us had our arm and leg bitten off by a Bull Shark - we wouldn’t want to go back into the water!? Not Paul De Gelder! Listen to episode 1 of our podcast (link in bio) and hear Paul talk first hand on what happened to him on the day that his life changed forever and how he doesn’t regret a single thing. node.text:
#Repost @realeliroth
・・・
I’ve spent years making this film in secrecy and can finally announce it to the world. On July 13th, on @discoveryplus @sharkweek  you can see the horrors I learned about the global shark slaughter. I’ve partnered with the top scientists, NGOs and activists @leonardodicaprio @nina and @michaelmuller7 to show the problem from all sides and present solutions we can all do to save sharks before they’re gone. This may be the scariest film I have ever made because it’s real, but it doesn’t have to be. Fifty years ago the world came together to save the whales, then it was dolphins , then orcas and now more than ever is the time for sharks. node.text:
This could be the most important movie you ever watch regarding our oceans. 

Make no mistake, much of the seafood eaten in the world is funding the destruction of our planet, supporting slavery and death, and pushing our own species towards extinction. 

Do what you think is right! 
I stopped supporting it all together. 
We can make a difference. 

#CommercialFishing #AnimalAgriculture #IsDestroyingOurPlanet
#EatNoShark #TheOcean #LeaveItAlone @seaspiracy

node.text:
Don’t forget you can now watch Shark Week to your hearts content whenever you like on @discoveryplus 
After 4 weeks on a live aboard boat in dinosaur country, Australia with @joeromeiro333 we got more then we bargained for. 
Chopper evacuations, Boat captain nearly getting killed, crocs stalking our boat at night, squid ink fights, i got blinded by a green sea turtle and that was the stuff they didn’t show in the program 😂 #SharkWeek #Sharks #Crocodiles #Australia #Travel #Adventure #Film #AustraliansInFilm

node.text:
Shot for XBOX, Fearless never made it to a series. 
@NatGeo played the pilot without even telling me or the production company that it was going to air, or letting us do promo’s for it. 
It was a massive let down but i guess that’s show business. 
I still think it would make a cracker of a show. 
What do you think? Rebrand & Rename?
Maybe each episode could be with a different celebrity or a rad co-host. 

#IdWatchIt #Fearless #Adventure #TV #Series 
#Life & #Death #Sharks #Bombs #Rescue #Rhinos

I got a rad little package from my friends @4ocean to help me while I’m smashing trash of the beach. 
They’ve successfully removed 11 million pounds of plastic thus far and ain’t slowing down. Give them a follow, check out their kit and help me help them help our ocean creatures. 🦾🤿
#DontBeATosser #Ocean #Plastic #Beach #CleanUp #Sharks #Conservation #Wildlife @recycleforveterans

@thedirtdownunder 

A baby Humpback Whale is struggling for its life while entangled in a shark net on the Gold Coast RIGHT NOW. 
Go to your favorite Podcast platform and listen to Episode 5 of @thedirtdownunder TO FIND OUT HOW YOU CAN HELP STOP THIS as @iamjuliawheeler abs myself talk with world famous shark expert @oceanramsey. Australia has run the longest marine cull in history (see footage shot in the last 24 hours) - absolutely disgraceful - Shark nets are even proven to be ineffective in a court of law. We discuss @envoyfilm and how this film highlights that! ACT NOW: listen to our podcast and watch @envoyfilm , and sign the petition to stop these traps at envoyfilm.com.au/
.
Footage by @scottwilsonimagery 
.
#shark #podcast #ocean #nature @spotifypodcasts @groundswellgiving @pauldegelder @bondiradio @juansharks #freediver #helpsavesharks #humpbackwhale #australia #goldcoast #byronbay #sydney #hawaii #whaleswim #picoftheday #inspire #motivation @oneoceandiving #ApexPredatorNotMonster

node.text:
Did you watching seaspiracy?
Did you hate it?
Did you think it was BS?
Did it open your eyes and make you want to change your eating habits?

@iamjuliawheeler  and i sat down with Ali Tabrizi the director and host of what had become one of @netflix most controversial documentaries and asked him the hard questions that everyone wants to know. 
Here’s what Julia had to say:

Well, I didn’t hold back during this interview and had to throw everything under the bus, including @iamalitabrizi the Director of @netflix top ten and highly controversial films, @seaspiracy with @pauldegelder who spent the majority of the interview looking like I just slapped him in the face. This film is out of control. But the allegations around the misinformation that the film presents are even more out of control. Watch @seaspiracy and listen to our latest podcast on @thedirtdownunder where we go deep and uncover the truth behind these crazy allegations (link in bio)  #podcast #freediver #hardcore #owch #boom
